<h1><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>About <%= application.name %></h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>About <%= application.name %></li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> is a complete family of free, friendly, self-hostable cloud-based sharing platforms, each of which has been optimized for a particular application. <%= application.name %> can help you to manage and share files, comments, photos, music, and other data. </p>

	<div class="attention"><div class="emphasis">Use <%= application.name %> to Set Up Your Own Personal Cloud</div></div>

	<h2><i class="fa fa-computer"></i>Setting Up Your Own <%= application.name %></h2>
	<p>Setting up your own platform is relatively easy. You will need some familiarity with the basics of web servers and tools such as Docker. If you're familiar with those tools, you should be able to get started setting up your own platform in just a few minutes. </p>

	<div class="alt section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-3">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/about/server.svg" />
				</div>
				<br />
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-9">
				<ol>
					<li>
						<h3>Select a Web Server</h3>
						<p>To set up and run your own <%= application.name %> platform, you will first need access to a <a href="#self-hosting">web server</a>. 
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Select a Platform</h3>
						<p>Select a platform that best suits your needs from the <a href="#platforms"><%= application.name %> family of platforms. </a></p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Download</h3>
						<p>Download your platform of choice.  <%= application.name %> platforms are open and free of charge. </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Install</h3>
						<p>To install the platform on your web server, either use the one step Docker installer or install the platorm manually. </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Configure</h3>
						<p>If desired, configure the platform for your server (mail settings, storage, third party authentication etc.) </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Brand</h3>
						<p>Brand the platform using your name, logo, preferred colors, fonts, etc. </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Create Account</h3>
						<p>Create an account on your platform.  Set up your user profile if you'd like. </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Invite</h3>
						<p>Invite your friends and colleagues to the platform. </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Connect</h3>
						<p>Connect with your friends and colleagues. </p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<h3>Collaborate and Share!</h3>
						<p>Collaborate, and share files, messages, photos, music, and more! </p>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<br />

	<p>Please consider joining us in the <a href="#welcome/we-can-do-it">host-it-yourself movement</a> and running your own personal cloud today! </p>
</div>